reviewText: Lucille Ball is hilarious in this 2 season set! Great episodes! They are not colorized as one may think from the cover but still great classic and comedy at its best!
Bought them for Grandma and Grandpa to have at their house for the grandkids.  We already have these and thoroughly enjoy them.
bought this as a gift and of course brand new.  cant find anything to complain about, episodes are commercial free and in great quality! a must have for anyone who loves the old I Love Lucy tv show.
Product came much faster then promised, great condition, brand new, would buy from seller again
